Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest sdpub toc

sdpub toc

Purpose:
  Print the archive TOC tree in reading order.

Usage:
  spinedigest sdpub toc --input <path> [--help|-h]

Output shape:
  - Document title first, when available
  - Indented TOC items
  - `[serial N]` markers on items linked to a serial summary

Notes:
  - The command fails if the archive has no TOC.
  - Empty TOCs print `No TOC items.`
